<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Parcel Picked Up</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #2d3748;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border-top: 4px solid #8b5cf6;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .pickup-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background-color: #8b5cf6;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .pickup-icon::after {
            content: 'üì¶';
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #1a202c;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .tracking-number {
            background-color: #faf5ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #8b5cf6;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .pickup-details {
            background-color: #faf5ff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #d8b4fe;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4a5568;
            min-width: 140px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #2d3748;
            text-align: right;
            max-width: 60%;
        }
        .status-badge {
            background-color: #d1fae5;
            color: #047857;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .driver-info {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        .driver-info h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        .progress-indicator {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .progress-step {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            flex: 1;
            position: relative;
        }
        .progress-step::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            left: 60%;
            width: 80%;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
        }
        .progress-step:last-child::after {
            display: none;
        }
        .progress-step.completed::after {
            background-color: #10b981;
        }
        .step-circle {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .step-circle.completed {
            background-color: #10b981;
            color: white;
        }
        .step-circle.current {
            background-color: #8b5cf6;
            color: white;
        }
        .step-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #7c3aed);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .support-info {
            background-color: #fef5e7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f6ad55;
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            body { padding: 10px; }
            .container { padding: 25px; }
            .detail-row { flex-direction: column; }
            .detail-value { text-align: left; margin-top: 5px; }
            .detail-label { min-width: auto; }
            .progress-indicator { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; }
            .progress-step::after { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="pickup-icon"></div>
        <h1>Package Picked Up!</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>

    <p>Great news! Your package has been picked up and is now on its way to the destination. üì¶üöö</p>

    <div class="tracking-number">
        Tracking Number: <%= trackingNumber %>
    </div>

    <div class="pickup-details">
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Pickup Location:</span>
            <span class="detail-value"><%= pickupLocation %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Pickup Time:</span>
            <span class="detail-value"><%= pickupTime %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Status:</span>
            <span class="detail-value"><span class="status-badge">‚óè In Transit</span></span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <% if (driverName && driverPhone) { %>
        <div class="driver-info">
            <h3>üöö Your Driver</h3>
            <p><strong>Driver:</strong> <%= driverName %></p>
            <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="tel:<%= driverPhone %>" style="color: #1e40af;"><%= driverPhone %></a></p>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="progress-indicator">
        <div class="progress-step completed">
            <div class="step-circle completed">‚úì</div>
            <div class="step-label">Order Placed</div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-step completed">
            <div class="step-circle completed">‚úì</div>
            <div class="step-label">Picked Up</div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-step">
            <div class="step-circle current">‚óè</div>
            <div class="step-label">In Transit</div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-step">
            <div class="step-circle">4</div>
            <div class="step-label">Delivered</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p>Your package is now in safe hands and on its way to the delivery address. We'll keep you updated with real-time tracking information as it progresses.</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= trackingUrl %>" class="button">Track Your Package</a>
    </div>

    <p>Thank you for choosing <%= appName %>. We're committed to delivering your package safely and on time!</p>

    <div class="support-info">
        <strong>Need Help?</strong><br>
        If you have any questions about your shipment, contact our support team at
        <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #d69e2e;"><%= supportEmail %></a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.<br>
    This email was sent regarding tracking number <%= trackingNumber %>
</div>
</body>
</html>